Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:53.26,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深く激しく　そっと優しく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:02:00.24,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突き動かして情熱に訴えて　ひとつになろうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:12.66,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳いだ目線　不埒な彷徨えるエゴイズム
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:17.98,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着飾った秘密のベール 脱がせてくれるのはあなた？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:20.74,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露骨に躍った欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.55,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは私のドコが理由なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:26.43,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私のナニに昂っているの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:29.80,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ待って！　少し妬けるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:35.48,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空より遠い　冥より深い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:40.74,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇の城より舞い降りしFreaky Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:47.48,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Death Sickleが指揮者ね　魅惑のレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:54.72,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突き刺さる心の十字架に　何を誓って戯れようか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:59.57,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焦らした指先　先駆けた誘惑の雫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:02.61,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糸を手繰って　すぐココに来て
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:08.37,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心から溢れ出した　甘い蜜に愛を這わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:13.92,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reason why kiss　離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:53.26,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深入而激烈 輕盈而溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:02:00.24,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放掉這股撩人的激情 合為一體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:12.66,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右飄忽的視線 搖擺不定的利己主義讓人又愛又恨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:17.98,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,褪下我身上這層秘密薄紗的人 會是你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:20.74,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那露骨的熊熊欲火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.55,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是因為我的哪個部分而點燃？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:26.43,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是因為我的什麼而高漲難耐？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:29.80,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦！差點被你燒著了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:35.48,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比天空還高遠 比冥府還幽深
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:40.74,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從黑暗城堡降臨的怪異女王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:47.48,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮者是鐮刀冥使 它奏響了魅惑的安魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:54.72,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對著直直插入心中的十字架 該許下什麼誓言來捉弄你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:59.57,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫人心癢難耐的指尖 呼之欲出的誘惑之滴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:02.61,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收緊命運的絲線 讓你立刻來到此處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:08.37,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓愛吸附在從內心中滿溢而出的甜汁蜜液之上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:13.92,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reason why kiss 永遠不分離
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:09.90,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋なんてもうしないって　何回も心に決めても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.19,0:22:14.87,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繰り返す性懲りもなく　それが恋だもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:22.10,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残念な結末だって　そんなこと気にしなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:27.02,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっとまた出会えるはず　赤い糸の先
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.48,0:22:33.04,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠い未来の自分へ　捧げたいのは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.51,0:22:41.96,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今この時をみんなで　全力で生きた証でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.53,0:22:48.59,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らが歩いてきた道には　満開の花が咲くから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.19,0:22:55.02,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう　輝いてなくちゃ嘘になってしまうでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.25,0:23:00.81,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見るもの聞くものすべてを　僕らは分かち合えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.42,0:23:06.31,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう　手をつないで行く　終わらない明日へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:09.90,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕多少次下定決心 再也不去碰什麼戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.19,0:22:14.87,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一次次不知悔改的重蹈覆轍 這就是所謂的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:22.10,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算結果並不如你所願 但是也不用太過於在意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:27.02,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的邂逅一定馬上就會出現 就在鮮紅絲線的那一頭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.48,0:22:33.04,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處於遙遠未來的自己 現在的我想要獻給她的..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.51,0:22:41.96,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是此時此刻大家一起 全力奮鬥過的證明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.53,0:22:48.59,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們一路走來的這段旅途之上 開滿了遍地的繁花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.19,0:22:55.02,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 如果不好好閃耀一下的話約定不就成了謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.25,0:23:00.81,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為眼睛看到耳朵聽到的一切 我們都會彼此分享
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.42,0:23:06.31,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 手牽著手一起前行 去到那永不終結的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良介！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有趕上..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？這是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 掉下來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良介 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“還”是什麼意思..結果還是會死對不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死啦..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.56,0:00:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:00:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.76,0:01:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.92,0:01:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們幾個..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會拯救良介的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用美菜擁有的特異者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良介會得救是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.88,0:01:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜..拜託妳了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是..是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請大家..多費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:24.88,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(920,600)}第11話 戀情成真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好懷念呢 媽媽的什錦蔬菜咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而插進來的劍還跑到了在我肚子裏的良介身上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好在大家願意救你一命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果OK就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得真輕描淡寫啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣才像媽媽的作風嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐 我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的..所謂的命運還真是殘酷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是莉薩菈小姐的同伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 雖然立場有一點不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良介 我進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和美菜的約會 準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好幹哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常適合妳哦 美菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須為了小良加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊張什麼的實在太浪費了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果美菜是從心底享受這次約會的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會很順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要用平時的美菜去應對就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好享受一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果特異者的能力覺醒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良介就一定會得救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對覺醒來說最有效的那個按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是來自良介先生的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好支援他倆的約會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現一只可以利用的狗狗！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裘兒 幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好令人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小良手牽手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候經常這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳啊 只要一放開手就搖搖晃晃看著好危險呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒..沒有那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是冒冒失失的 很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小良..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良介不會得救？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的壽命從出生之時就已經決定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺憾的是..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就把我的生命讓給良介..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種生命的轉讓是無法實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那良介他..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走完人生的加賀良介的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將曝露在凈化之火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到凈化之後 他的能量就會被回收
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:09:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而靈魂一旦脫離肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法再次回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉薩菈小姐她們不是說..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她們可能想用那個特異者的力量來反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按我說百分之百不可能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按我說是有可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我這種研究者的話來說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的事象皆無絕對可言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信莉薩菈小姐她們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是完全無能為力的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於近來社會的特殊狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可能會出現放映突然中止的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請諒解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為看起來不像小良要看的那類電影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾換個口味也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要兩個人一起看的話 只有這個最適合了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:22.61,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放映中請安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好地在約會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一個適合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得呢 小良？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:24.74,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古古拉的寶劍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候都把這本書翻爛了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 第123版呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個還有在賣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色一下子就會用完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紅色啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:11:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細一想 買個一模一樣的反而比較便宜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小良幫我抓的才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個冰淇淋..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始還是選妳那個口味比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看吧 所以我才說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 只可以嚐一口哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然該選那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬太大塊了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..不 沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界都要嫉妒這一對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 看來已經不需要我們了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉薩菈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:12:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在那硬撐..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還蠻貴的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:12.73,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(305,260)}{\frz352}披肩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:12.73,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(305,390)}{\frz352}連衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試穿看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜 怎樣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打開了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小良的女朋友嗎..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為實在適合妳..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給..給我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小良給的禮物 這可能是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小良
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我穿上這個 能不能再帶我出來玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小良
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的小良..帥氣過頭了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為平時的我都遜爆了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒..沒有那回事啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小良一直都很帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小時候就一直..！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我一直都喜歡著那樣的小良啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我本來就很清楚..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天我更加明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對小良..非常非常地喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小良對我..是怎麼想的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜..我也..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣良介先生就會得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！剛才那是..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人..吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人 怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小良對我..是怎麼想的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜..我也..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉薩菈！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良介！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你 不想得救了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉薩菈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼拒絕了美菜的告白？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我還是撒不了謊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謊話？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為..我喜歡的是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你根本..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妳的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是再糟糕不過了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一上來就被捅了一劍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任性蠻橫..又總是居高臨下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知怎麼地就是非常在意妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著妳拼命尋找特異者的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就總想著有一天一定要讓妳露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為對你來說 所有的女孩子都是寶藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我只不過是其中一員而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始可能是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我從莉薩菈那裡感受到的..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和至今為止感受到的都不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！我對你根本一點都沒有想法！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.53,0:18:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在馬上就向美菜道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她解釋那是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後跟她說你喜歡她 緊緊抱住她！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣下去的話會死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快變成情侶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快抱美人上床啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做愛做的事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓我..為難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良介？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實想..多跟妳...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良介先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉..莉薩菈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是說良介能得救嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又..被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:20:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小良 要活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良介先生他..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小良..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小良！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良介..？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良介！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太傻了 良介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的..太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.23,0:23:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會讓你死的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.34,0:23:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 良介！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.23,0:23:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 預感到一股有些不符這個節目風格的正統感動..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼可能嘞！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級無敵難為情的命運正在等著莉薩菈呢嘞！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.17,0:23:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？那是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.49,0:23:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒聽說啊
